title: If You're Not Doing What You Can, You'll Never Do What You Want, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO252
itunes:title: If You're Not Doing What You Can, You'll Never Do What You Want, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO252
description: Everybody has dreams for their future. But not everybody understands that what you hope to do on a much higher level later, you can begin to do right now. The guy who wants to someday speak to millions can give a talk to his 7 employees today. The girl who wants to perform on stage in Nashville someday can sing at a local country bar this weekend.  Bottom line: when it comes to your dreams, if you're not doing what you can do now, you'll never do what you want to do later.
